== 製作 ==
[[File:Ben-Stiller-(MS1411200222).jpg|thumb]]所有之{{link-en|紅時製作公司|Red Hour Productions}}製作，史提勒除了擔任執行製作，亦有客串演出。]]
本劇惡搞了人氣實境節目《{{link-en|與卡戴珊一家同行|Keeping Up with the Kardashians}}》以及時代劇《[[唐頓莊園|唐頓莊園]]》，並將兩者融合，諷刺其社會階級關係與風氣。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Cathcart|first1=Olivia|title=A conversation with Natasha Leggero|url=http://thelaughbutton.com/features/conversation-natasha-leggero/|website=The Laugh Button|accessdate=2015-06-16|date=2014-09-12|quote=It’s kind of like Keeping Up With The Kardashians meets Downton Abbey, I guess. Riki Lindhome and I play these rich and sort of tacky heiresses who are just trying to get into society and become famous, which is hard in 1902 because there’s no TV or media.|archive-date=2019-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190707124414/https://thelaughbutton.com/features/conversation-natasha-leggero/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年1月15日，[[喜劇中心|喜劇中心]]預訂來自[[班·史提勒|班·史提勒]]所有之{{link-en|紅時製作公司|Red Hour Productions}}，由喜劇女演員{{link-en|娜塔莎·拉格羅|Natasha Leggero}}與{{link-en|芮琪·琳達馮|Riki Lindhome}}開創兼主演、《{{le|醉酒史|Drunk History}}》{{le|傑瑞米·康納|Jeremy Konner}}執導之喜劇試播集，三人也將共同擔任執行製作。<ref name="Pilot">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/01/comedy-central-orders-natasha-leggero-pilot-from-red-hour-standup-special-664490/|title=Comedy Central Orders Natasha Leggero Pilot From Red Hour & Standup Special|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2014-01-15|accessdate=2017-04-26|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130231551/https://deadline.com/2014/01/comedy-central-orders-natasha-leggero-pilot-from-red-hour-standup-special-664490/|dead-url=no}}</ref>本劇以實境秀風格呈現，聚焦於新港第一豪門，一個對社會毫無貢獻，卻擁有龐大財產的白拉寇家族。<ref name="Pilot"/>拉格羅與琳達馮將飾演維多利亞時代的貴婦，也就是白拉寇家族姊妹花莉莉安與碧翠絲，身處1902年的她們，只關心自己的外表、被邀請參加什麼派對以及如何成名。<ref name="Pilot"/>6月9日，喜劇中心正式給予本劇系列預訂，而史提勒、{{link-en|黛比·莉布林|Debbie Liebling}}、{{link-en|史都華·康菲爾德|Stuart Cornfeld}}與麥克·羅森史坦均將共同擔任執行製作。<ref name="Series Order">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/06/comedy-central-another-period-idiotsitter-inside-amy-schumer-review-triptank-786746/|title=Comedy Central Gives Series Orders To ‘Another Period’ & ‘Idiotsitter’, Renews ‘Inside Amy Schumer,’ Review’ & ‘TripTank’|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2014-06-09|accessdate=2017-04-26|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223070733/https://deadline.com/2014/06/comedy-central-another-period-idiotsitter-inside-amy-schumer-review-triptank-786746/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

9月30日，喜劇中心預訂了本劇10集，並由{{link-en|紅時製作公司|Red Hour Productions}}、拉格羅／琳達馮製作公司與康納製作公司共同製作。

2015年8月18日，喜劇中心宣布續訂第2季。<ref name=seasontworenewal>{{cite web|last1=Pedersen|first1=Erik|title=‘Another Period’ Renewed For Season 2 On Comedy Central|url=http://deadline.com/2015/08/another-period-renewed-comedy-central-natasha-leggero-riki-lindhome-1201500714/|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2015-08-19|archive-date=2019-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190707124412/https://deadline.com/2015/08/another-period-renewed-comedy-central-natasha-leggero-riki-lindhome-1201500714/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年5月23日，喜劇中心在第2季首播前，提前續訂第3季。<ref name="Season 3 Renewal">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/tv/news/another-period-renewed-season-3-comedy-central-1201780990/|title=‘Another Period’ Renewed For Season 2 On Comedy Central|publisher=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]|last=Prudom|first=Laura|date=2016-05-23|accessdate=2016-05-30|archive-date=2019-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031175729/https://variety.com/2016/tv/news/another-period-renewed-season-3-comedy-central-1201780990/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

